data.description: Welcome to the Highlands! This historic Victorian 3 family is conveniently located just minutes away from the proposed train station, highway access, South Coast hospital, beautiful waterfront attractions, restaurant's, schools and much more! The first floor unit features an open floor plan with 1.5 bath, beautiful architectural details, original woodwork, stained glass windows, unique pocket doors, fireplace, crown molding and a huge wrap around porch. Each unit offers very spacious bedrooms and living space with gleaming hardwood floors throughout, crown molding and beautiful water views. All separate utilities and off St parking available. This charming Victorian is a must see!
